---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Pixel River <span>Studio</span></h1>
  <p class="tagline">Indie Games inspired by 2000s classics — modernized, 3D, with real depth.</p>
</section>

<section class="game-teaser">
  <h2>RiverTycoon</h2>
  <p>From broke indie dev to tech CEO. Grind jobs, buy gear, build your empire — in a world full of iFoons, Samsong devices and Damazon Crime deliveries.</p>
  <div class="badges">
    <span class="badge">In Development</span>
    <span class="badge">Unity 6</span>
    <span class="badge">Mobile</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="latest-devlog">
  <h2>Latest DevLog</h2>
  {% set latestPost = collections.devlog[0] %}
  {% if latestPost %}
    <article class="post-card">
      <time>{{ latestPost.date | dateDisplay }}</time>
      <h3><a href="{{ latestPost.url }}">{{ latestPost.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <p>{{ latestPost.data.summary }}</p>
    </article>
    <a href="/devlog/" class="btn">Alle DevLogs &rarr;</a>
  {% else %}
    <p>DevLog-Eintraege folgen in Kuerze.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>

<section class="social">
  <h2>Follow the Build</h2>
  <div class="social-links">
    <a href="https://github.com/PatrickRoller81" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
    <a href="https://twitter.com/RiverTycoonDev" target="_blank">X / Twitter</a>
    <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@RiverTycoonDev" target="_blank">TikTok</a>
  </div>
</section>
